<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.4.2">
<l>muṉṉam kuṟaḷuruvāy mūvaṭimaṇ koṇṭaḷanta</l>
<l>maṉṉaṉ caritaikkē mālākip poṉpayantēṉ</l>
<l>poṉṉam kaḻikkāṉal puḷḷiṉaṅkāḷ pullāṇi</l>
<l>aṉṉamāy nūlpayantāṟ kāṅkitaṉaic ceppumiṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Becoming crazy for the tales of the king who, previously with a dwarf body,</l>
<l>Measured and took three feet of earth, I have produced a gold [complexion].</l>
<l>[You] flocks of birds on the shore with lovely, golden shoals,</l>
<l>Please tell this there in Pullāṇi to him who as a swan produced the book.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
